# Titanic Passenger Survival – Tableau Story

This Tableau Public story explores how passenger **class**, **gender**, **age group**, and **family status** impacted survival during the Titanic disaster.
The goal was to combine data visualization with narrative storytelling to create a compelling, insight-driven experience.

