## 🔍 Key Insights
- **Gender + Class**: Women had higher survival rates across all classes, with 1st-class women the most likely to survive.
- **Age**: Children had the highest survival rate overall; seniors had the lowest.
- **Family Status**: Passengers with family had significantly higher survival odds than those traveling alone.

